process : 
---------
>>> ps -l | list process of current session.

>>> ps -f | List process of full formate .

>>> ps -e | List all process.

>>> ps -u user_name | List process of user_name.

>>> ps -x | Show processes that do not have a controlling terminal (like daemons: MySQL, nginx, etc.)

>>> ps -p [PID] | Display process information of PID
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
----------------------------------Kill the process ------------------------------------------
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
>>> Kill [ps_id] | kill the process ID. 

>>> kill -9 [ps_id] | kill the process forcely.
